{"tid":2464234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父親因買錯波鞋被毆打","createTime":"2021-03-27T09:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:21:44.000Z","uid":42188,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6545c2416db19d24b2a03e255e0026762dd668e9","tid":2464234,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"中国公安於27日以傷害罪嫌疑，在北京逮捕了一名以新疆棉花毆打父親的的少年（15歲）。由於母親看到兒子的暴行而馬上加以阻止，父親只受了輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n根據調查，少年和父親（42歲）約好，要父親替他購買於3月27日發售的Nike限量版波鞋。不過從早上就去排隊的父親，卻買回了李寧波鞋，這讓少年相當惱火。在吃早飯時，少年拿起放在鞋架上的FILA波鞋內的新疆棉花（長30厘米），不斷毆打父親。<br />\n<br />\n聽到父親的慘叫的母親急忙來阻止了少年，不過父親的額頭還是受了輕微的毆傷。少年被附近接到報告的警察逮捕。在調查中少年供訴到：「一想到他那麼早出去到底去排了什麼隊，就惱火的不得了。」<br />\n<br />\n警視廳表示，今後類似這種由於親子間對愛国的理解溝通不充分，而引發的暴力事件，還將有可能發生，請大家引以為戒。"},{"pid":"68736d2764e566ab8ea02f634274183a1b4e893b","tid":2464234,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23c5f03d63e0e95f51006f1e9e95225a7d38f94","tid":2464234,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"警視廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5947029d8c62f1767988955fab9c5a7702ccd888","tid":2464234,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">卻買回了李寧波鞋</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400ea739c283a682de2ab9f20a74086c72bbec06","tid":2464234,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:17:37.000Z","msg":"咁都叫新聞，叫老豆買李寧變左NIKE比仔打先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be21e4eb1ba285590e59d3256c6bf3ac9d302ab","tid":2464234,"uid":272271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"PS5個篇？"}]}